title: TUESDAY - NFL trade deadline 2020
itunes:title: TUESDAY - NFL trade deadline 2020
description:
Week 8 wrapped up Monday night in a game that came down to the wire (0:06) as the Buccaneers held off the Giants. Tom Brady talked about the close call (1:08). With today's trade deadline (1:57) fast approaching some big names could be on the move including Texans wide receiver Will Fuller. Could he be joining Aaron Rodgers in Green Bay? The NFL could be considering an expanded playoff system (2:30). We'll break down the possible format. And, the 49ers hit hard by the injury bug again (3:56) as Jimmy Garoppolo and George Kittle will be on the shelf for awhile
